    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Deserts having summers that are moderately long and dry, and like hot deserts, the winters normally bring low concentrations of rainfall. Summer temperatures usually average between 21-27 degrees C. Soil may be sandy or rocky.</Note_Text>
